2016/mikrocenzus_2016_12.pdf|title=Mikrocenzus 2016 \u2013 12. Nemzetis\u00e9gi adatok|trans-title=2016 microcensus \u2013 12. Ethnic data|language=hu|work=Hungarian Central Statistical Office|location=Budapest|year=2018|accessdate=10 January 2019|isbn=978-963-235-542-9}}</ref>\n }}\n| ethnic_groups_year                = microcensus 2016\n| religion_year                = census 2011\n| religion_ref                = <ref name=\"Census2011det\" />\n| religion                = {{ublist |item_style=white-space:nowrap; |54.3% [[Christianity]]| {{bulleted list |39% [[Catholicism]]|13.8% [[Protestantism]]|3.3% other Christians|0.2% [[Orthodox Church]]}}|0.1% [[Judaism]]|0.05% [[Buddhism in Hungary|Buddhism]]|0.01% other|18.2% not religious|27.2% unanswered}}\n| demonym                = [[Hungarian people|Hungarian]]\n| government_type                = [[Unitary state|Unitary]] [[Dominant-party system|dominant-party]] [[Parliamentary system|parliamentary]] [[republic]]\n| leader_title1                = [[President of Hungary|President]]\n| leader_name1                = [[J\u00e1nos \u00c1der]]\n| leader_title2                = [[Prime Minister of Hungary|Prime Minister]]\n| leader_name2                = [[Viktor Orb\u00e1n]]\n| leader_title3                = [[List of Speakers of the National Assembly of Hungary|Speaker of the National&nbsp;Assembly]]\n| leader_name3                = [[L\u00e1szl\u00f3 K\u00f6v\u00e9r]]\n| legislature                = ''[[National Assembly (Hungary)|Orsz\u00e1ggy\u0171l\u00e9s]]''\n| sovereignty_type                = [[History of Hungary|Foundation]]\n| established_event1                = [[Principality of Hungary]]\n| established_date1                = 895<ref>{{cite book|title=Encyclopedia Americana: Heart to India|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=igzYAAAAMAAJ|volume=1|year=2006|publisher=Scholastic Library Pub.|isbn=978-0-7172-0139-6|page=581}}</ref>\n| established_event2                = [[Kingdom of Hungary|Christian Kingdom]]\n| 