s=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n|-\n!scope=\"col\"|Region\n!scope=\"col\"|Date\n!scope=\"col\"|Format\n!scope=\"col\"|Label\n!scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\"|{{abbr|Ref.|References}}\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|Various\n|September 27, 2018\n|{{hlist|Digital download|streaming}}\n|Interscope Records\n|style=\"text-align:center\"| <ref name=\"Truitt\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Italy\n| October 5, 2018\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[Contemporary hit radio]]\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[Universal Music Group]]\n|style=\"text-align:center\"|  <ref name=\"earone\">{{cite web|url=https://www.earone.it/news/lady_gaga_bradley_cooper_shallow_radio_date_05_10_2018_31437711/|title=Lady Gaga & Bradley Cooper \u2013 Shallow (Radio Date: 05-10-2018)|language=it|accessdate=October 10, 2018|work=Earone Radio|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181011133319/https://www.earone.it/news/lady_gaga_bradley_cooper_shallow_radio_date_05_10_2018_31437711/|archive-date=October 11, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|United Kingdom\n| October 13, 2018\n|style=\"text-align:center\"| <ref name=\"ukchr\">{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/radio2/playlist|title=Radio 2 New Music: October 13, 2018|accessdate=October 10, 2018|publisher=[[BBC Radio 2]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180929090541/http://www.bbc.co.uk/radio2/playlist|archivedate=September 29, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"2\"|United States\n| October 15, 2018\n| [[Adult contemporary music|Hot adult contemporary]]\n|rowspan=\"2\"|Interscope Records\n|style=\"text-align:center\"| <ref name=\"hotacadds\">{{cite web|url=https://www.allaccess.com/hot-modern-ac/future-releases|title=Hot/Modern/AC > Future Releases|accessdate=October 10, 2018|publisher=All Access Radio Group|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180918151411/https://www.allaccess.com/hot-modern-ac/future-releases|archivedate=September 18, 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n| October 16, 2018\n|rowspan=\"2\"| Contemporary hit radio\n|style=\"text-align:center\"| <ref name=\"chradds\">{{cite web|url=https://www.allaccess.com/top40-mainstream/future-releases|title=Top 40/Mainstream > Future Releases|accessdate=October 10, 2018|publisher=All Access Radio Group|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171130080259/https://www.allaccess.com/top40-mainstream/future-releases|archivedate=November 30, 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|Australia\n| October 18, 2018\n| Universal Music Group\n|style=\"text-align:center\"| <ref name=\"ausradio\">{{cite web|url=https://themusicnetwork.com/charts/issues/1212/1212-most-added-to-radio/|title=Issue 1212: Most Added to Radio|accessdate=October 19, 2018|magazine=[[The Music Network]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181019100438/https://themusicnetwork.com/charts/issues/1212/1212-most-added-to-radio/|archivedate=October 19, 2018}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==See also==\n{{Wikipedia books|A Star Is Born (2018 film)}}\n{{div col}}\n* [[Artists with the most number-ones on the U.S. Dance Club Songs chart]]\n* [[List of Billboard Hot 100 top-ten singles in 2018|List of ''Billboard'' Hot 100 top-ten singles in 2018]]\n* [[List of Billboard Hot 100 number-one singles of 2019|List of ''Billboard'' Hot 100 number-one singles of 2019]]\n* [[List of Canadian Hot 100 number-one singles of 2019]]\n* [[List of most-streamed songs on Spotify]]\n* [[List of number-one singles of 2018 (Australia)]]\n* [[List of number-one singles of 2019 (Australia)]]\n* [[List of number-one hits of 2018 (Austria)]]\n* [[List of number-one hits of 2019 (Denmark)]]\n* [[List of number-one singles of the 2010s (Hungary)]]\n* [[List of number-one singles of 2018 (Ireland)]]\n* [[List of number-one singles from the 2010s (New Zealand)]]\n* [[List of number-one songs in Norway#2019|List of number-one songs in Norway (2019)]]\n* [[List of number-one singles of 2018 (Portugal)]]\n* [[Scottish Singles and Albums Charts#2018|List of number-one singles of 2018 (Scotland)]]\n* [[List of number-one 